1                   PLC Control Sequences

A PLC sequence controls each system component. Each sequence interlocks with the next to ensure correct operation of the complete monorail system.

2                   Soiled System Sequence Tables

Important Note: Only a competent engineer should change sequence steps. Misuse could result in personal injury or damage to the system! If there any doubts then please contact Supertrack
Tel: +44 (0)1295 221221 Fax: +44 (0)1295 221222.

The following tables describe the operation of each system component. The Action shows the output for the current step and Moved on to next step shows the inputs required for the sequence to go to the next (another) step.

Tel: +44 (0)1295 221221 Fax: +44 (0)1295 221222.

The following tables describe the operation of each system component. The Action shows the output for the current step and Moved on to next step shows the inputs required for the sequence to go to the next (another) step.
